title: All About That Bass by DanielaDearest on NA
body:
My friend DanielaDearest has a parody of Meghan Trainor's All About That Bass called Going Back to Base, it's really good and I hope she gets more attention and recognition than she has at the moment. She has talent that I think could come into use with more support from fans and outsiders. ^^

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V-eI9HndXnw
